snippet.title: Wonderbook Book of Spells Live Demo E3
snippet.description:
Sony demoed the first title for their new "Wonderbook" peripheral. It's called Book of Spells, and is based on the Harry Potter series.
More E3 coverage at: http://www.gamingtrend.com
